{"word":"G4046 - περιποιέομαι - peripoiéomai - per-ee-poy-eh'-om-ahee - Purchase","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιποιέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">peripoiéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-poy-eh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Purchase</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சம்பாதி, அடை"},{"paragraph":"1. to preserve for oneself life"},{"paragraph":"2. to get for oneself, purchase"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G4160 - ποιέω - poiéō - poy-eh'-o/4160\">G4160</a>; to <i>make around oneself</i>, that is, <i>acquire</i> (<i>buy</i>): - purchase.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}